---
import Card from "./Card/index.astro";
---
<Card colSpan="md:col-span-1" rowSpan="md:row-span-8" title="About me">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
    <div class="text-sm font-light">
      <p>
        With two decades of deep-rooted experience in semiconductor manufacturing, my journey spans from developing C# solutions on the factory floor to directing enterprise systems that drive <b class="font-semibold">$2B+ in annual revenue</b>. I've seen what happens when integration fails at scale, and I've built the infrastructure to make sure it doesn't.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="text-sm font-light">
      <p class="mb-2">Core Enterprise Expertise:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
        <li>C# / .NET — since 2003</li>
        <li>MS SQL / T-SQL</li>
        <li>webMethods (Software AG)</li>
        <li>SAP</li>
        <li>B2B / EDI Integration</li>
        <li>MES Systems</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="text-sm font-light">
      <p class="mb-2">Current Focus & Innovation:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
        <li>Multi-LLM orchestration</li>
        <li>n8n workflow automation</li>
        <li>AI-powered knowledge systems</li>
        <li>Local LLM deployment (Ollama / LM Studio)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      Lately, I've been rebuilding how I think. Not just how I work.
    </p>
  </div>
</Card>
